OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew rules on gambling      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadverts ban celebrities and
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsports stars               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Footballers, celebrities and social    
OL,6, media influencers will be banned from  
OL,7, gambling adverts under new rules.      
OL,9,FFrom October, gambling companies will  
OL,10,Fnot allowed to use stars to target     
OL,11,Funder-18s, The Committee for           
OL,12,FAdvertising Practice said.             
OL,14,FAnyone with a "strong appeal" for young
OL,15,Fpeople, such as footballer Cristiano   
OL,16,FRonaldo and Love Island star Chris     
OL,17,FHughes, must not appear in the adverts.
OL,19,FThe body representing betting firms    
OL,20,Fsaid it welcomed the new rules.        
